Package proseccoCoding.TLN.model

Class Country

  • java.lang.Object
    • proseccoCoding.TLN.model.Country
  • public class Country
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a country with all its trusted providers (that provide services). Every country must be identified by its international code of two characters.
